    <h2>COVID-19 UPDATE: Virtual TT 2021</h2>
    <p>
      Due to ongoing restrictions related to COVID-19, we will be holding the Castle to Hanauma Bay TT as a one day virtual challenge. This event is sanctioned by USAC and will be part of the year long ASBRA 2021 Point Series.
    </p>
