  <div id="registration" class="floating-section">
    <h2>Registration (2021)</h2>
    <p>Registration is $10 for all participants, and no USAC License is required. Registration is available Online @ <a href="https://www.bikereg.com/castle-to-hanauma-2021" target="">bikereg.com</a> (through the day of the event: March 6th 2021)</p>
    <p><em>
      All participants must sign the USA Cycling Event Release form.<br />
    </em></p>
